shortDescription: The toys are back and ready to have another unforgettable laugh-out-loud adventure, so get dressed! In this Toy Story Buzz Lightyear Hoodie join space ranger Buzz Lightyear and his friends Sheriff Woody, Jessie the cowgirl, the green Aliens, Mr. and Mrs. Potato Head, Slinky Dog, Hamm the piggy bank, Bo-Peep, and the lovable toy horse Bullseye on their latest journey out of the toy box, to infinity and beyond. With your child on their side, these faithful toys from the iconic and groundbreaking Disney Pixar Toy Story films will be singing “You’ve Got a Friend in Me” in no time. Your little one will look so adorable and cool in this cute, comfy and stylish long sleeve graphic hooded sweatshirt featuring their favorite animated movies that they’ll always love wearing it.
